name: TOMI IRONY
description:
Tomi Irony wake from the dead in the electrical cemetery, where unknown corpses and debris of the spaceship and other gizmo waste gathered. made from 15%  recycled electrical stuff, 75% iron and metal and 10% human organs: The hair, THe moustache and goatee and ring and middle fingers.

Sometimes people think he is insane because he is frowning all the time, or maybe he is just made from an Iron, how can he put a curve on his mouth? But he does not care what other says, as long as he can play metalic sonic of primitive sound from his guitar. alone, in the cemetery.
